Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.04,0:00:11.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來那個小姑娘已經有保鏢跟著啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.10,0:00:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到木葉的護衛這麼快就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.02,0:00:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過四個人而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.97,0:00:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕鬆就能解決了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.58,0:00:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後從小姑娘那把禁術給奪過來 頭領
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.71,0:00:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心急吃不了熱豆腐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.45,0:00:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.48,0:00:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個禁術對於我們而言比金錢更重要
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.55,0:00:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不容有失
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.95,0:00:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是上次大戰中發揮了巨大威力的術
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.85,0:00:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能搶到手的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.24,0:00:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們這東拼西湊的賊匪集團
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.01,0:00:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為一國之主將不再是幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.14,0:00:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是那幫木葉忍者…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.47,0:00:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禁術在他們手中…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.73,0:00:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.20,0:00:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前代火影大人同役之行者之間
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.79,0:00:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾有過將禁術保護到底的秘密約定
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.24,0:01:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而木葉只是守護著那個約定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.71,0:01:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然有那樣的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.46,0:01:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些護衛一定相當強了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.24,0:01:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是 估計還會有其他增援趕來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.72,0:01:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南鄉 弁天 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.54,0:01:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒開打 你們就長他人志氣滅自己威風嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.54,0:01:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你不僅是外表 連大腦也不好使
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.86,0:01:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.32,0:01:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要考慮各種的可能性 用腦子分析問題
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.46,0:01:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許內訌 又忘了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.16,0:01:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是一個團隊 少了哪一個都不行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.67,0:01:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是 這樣的團隊再加上四人的合體忍術
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.97,0:01:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能在這亂世中生存下來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.95,0:01:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.57,0:01:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有什麼好慌張的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.66,0:01:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正他們的目的地是土蜘蛛一族的村落
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.38,0:01:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那幫木葉的忍者只要一抵達目的地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.31,0:01:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便會自動離去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.53,0:01:58.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 回到到村裡不就更麻煩了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.25,0:02:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤星…你還太嫩了 不懂人情世故
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.97,0:02:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個禁術對於我們而言是寶貝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.19,0:02:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於那幫正經人士們來說 則是危險的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.43,0:04:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是幹啥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.89,0:04:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是我要問的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.84,0:04:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼還跟著我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.94,0:04:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼啊 身為護衛這是理所當然的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.36,0:04:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都說過多少遍了 不需要護衛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.65,0:04:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會自己保護自己的安全
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.07,0:04:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木葉的各位 請回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.60,0:04:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.70,0:04:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也不能說句「明白了」 然後就回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.27,0:04:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不行呢 真的不需要你們管我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.82,0:04:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是要管你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.02,0:04:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是在護衛而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.21,0:04:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人 這就如她所言 我們回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.09,0:04:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.36,0:04:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.70,0:04:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.96,0:05:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣能行嗎 敵人不是還在附近嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.98,0:05:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.74,0:05:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 我們這就回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.62,0:05:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.82,0:05:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了 快拿掉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.27,0:05:29.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.83,0:05:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛…那…那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.63,0:05:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是山螞蟥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.92,0:05:37.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這附近似乎經常出現
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.15,0:05:39.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從天而降也不足為奇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.14,0:05:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從天而降…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.98,0:05:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.98,0:05:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人要多加小心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.64,0:05:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嗎突然發彪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.61,0:05:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人請留在我身邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.98,0:05:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不敢碰那種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.31,0:05:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行…絕對無法忍受
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.11,0:06:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那種東西掉下來的話 就請鳴人幫我擋住它
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.40,0:06:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說不需要護衛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.65,0:06:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到走出這座森林為止啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.39,0:06:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.34,0:06:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.68,0:06:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你沒轍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.42,0:06:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過仔細一想
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.48,0:06:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你們不出現的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.75,0:06:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就該由詩形大人護送我了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.66,0:06:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩形 就是會用不可思議之術的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.59,0:06:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位大人是我的師傅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.71,0:06:38.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想像詩形大人那樣強大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.01,0:06:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,師傅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.11,0:06:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂的師傅 一個個都不正常
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.49,0:06:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就拿我的師傅來說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.98,0:06:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又好色又輕浮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.04,0:06:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此外還自以為是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.31,0:07:02.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但話說回來 作為忍者還是相當了不起的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.88,0:07:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,值得信賴 比誰都溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.80,0:07:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說人不可貌相
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.47,0:07:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過真希望能有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.30,0:07:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也能成為那樣的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.82,0:07:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人也很喜歡師傅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.19,0:07:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.11,0:07:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰會喜歡那樣的色鬼啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.25,0:07:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想變得像詩形大人一樣厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.92,0:07:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我能變得強大的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.71,0:07:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能游刃有餘地使用爺爺為我留下的忍術了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.46,0:07:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.22,0:07:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能光復土蜘蛛一族了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.19,0:07:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不過是個孩子 背負這麼多也不容易
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.84,0:07:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你師傅跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.50,0:07:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.87,0:07:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知為何 詩形大人特別不喜歡稱他為師傅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.65,0:07:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐井 這是怎麼回事 太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.70,0:08:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再扔螞蟥了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.69,0:08:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是說再來個更大一點的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.70,0:08:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是嗎…那麼就…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.10,0:08:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 給我適可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.48,0:08:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋佐井 你幹啥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.08,0:08:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好分辨我的手勢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.76,0:08:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就能恢復之前閒雲野鶴的狀態了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.86,0:08:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果跟那傢伙一起 應該沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.13,0:08:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那股查克拉… 應該不會吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.48,0:09:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.26,0:09:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快來我們的要塞療傷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.19,0:09:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來追緝者沒有跟來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.73,0:09:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷勢也差不多痊癒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.70,0:09:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也該…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.28,0:10:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請收我做徒弟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.01,0:10:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前些日子看見師傅的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.47,0:10:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打心底裡敬佩不已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.23,0:10:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,師傅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.27,0:10:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 詩形師傅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.94,0:10:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准再叫第二次
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.02,0:10:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.41,0:10:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准再稱呼我為師傅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.10,0:10:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.14,0:10:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有任何收徒弟的意願
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.21,0:10:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩形大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.22,0:10:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是說 忘恩負義咯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.91,0:10:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白吃白喝真的可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.45,0:11:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼今晚的霸王餐該吃些什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.63,0:11:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪裡學到的這些討厭的手段
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.20,0:11:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是遁兵衛告訴我的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.25,0:11:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我拜師學藝遭拒絕時就這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.10,0:11:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位大叔是同謀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.36,0:11:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 對於從未做過任何修行的傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.67,0:11:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍術的話我在遁兵衛那受教過一點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.66,0:11:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就讓那位大叔教你不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.47,0:11:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有那麼一點不夠啊 所以才來拜託您的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.73,0:11:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 在池裡走幾步試試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.01,0:11:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在池裡 明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.54,0:11:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這水平的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.37,0:11:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我離開之前也不指望能成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.57,0:11:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩形大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.09,0:11:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.45,0:11:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩形大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.61,0:12:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一整晚都在練習嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.44,0:12:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 這樣就能收我為徒了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.26,0:12:08.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 這種程度才剛剛開始
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.14,0:12:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是這個忍術
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.66,0:12:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水遁.水亂波
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.58,0:12:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.64,0:12:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不達到這種程度就別想成為我的徒弟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.73,0:12:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.71,0:12:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水遁.水亂波
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.10,0:12:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水遁.水亂波
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.66,0:12:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.87,0:12:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個術沒有水屬性的查克拉是使不出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.36,0:12:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可別怪我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.30,0:12:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雨了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.26,0:12:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩形大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.77,0:12:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠太近了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.71,0:12:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.72,0:12:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水遁.水亂波
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.97,0:13:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就能收我為徒了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.75,0:13:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.59,0:13:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 還差得遠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.11,0:13:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 詩形大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.61,0:13:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就估計你該來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.57,0:13:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 就饒過我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.03,0:13:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煽動那孩子 到底打算幹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.02,0:13:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個小小的請求
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.23,0:13:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何請留在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.85,0:13:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫我保護螢小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.49,0:13:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還真是個麻煩的人情債啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.24,0:13:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螢小姐是命運之子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.38,0:13:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您那打倒敵人的非凡身手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.76,0:13:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正說明了您不是普通人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.64,0:13:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且更重要的是您別無他求
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.95,0:13:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如您所見 我已到古稀之年
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.46,0:14:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為您徒弟的話 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.11,0:14:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螢小姐的人身安全就能得到保障
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.25,0:14:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請無論如何也要答應我這個請求啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.77,0:14:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.57,0:14:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該能感覺到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.32,0:14:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正被人追殺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.49,0:14:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死神正在我的周圍蠢蠢欲動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.30,0:14:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎能在如此環境下收留那個孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.90,0:14:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.94,0:14:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還要以師徒關係…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.12,0:14:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼能行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.04,0:14:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,師傅 您打算幹嗎 師傅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.70,0:14:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,師…師傅…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.75,0:15:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不小心打了個盹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.06,0:15:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們真的能成為一國之主嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.67,0:15:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.32,0:15:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 赤星
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.73,0:15:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便賣掉也能得到一筆供一生浮華享樂的錢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.15,0:15:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.30,0:15:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心點 附近似乎有人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.70,0:15:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.89,0:15:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.61,0:15:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.80,0:15:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.37,0:15:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.27,0:16:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來不像是木葉的援軍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.28,0:16:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道這傢伙也想得到禁術…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.90,0:16:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然知道禁術的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.28,0:16:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說你們是賊匪集團了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.84,0:16:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那個禁術真有那麼厲害嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.89,0:16:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也對它有些興趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.32,0:16:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 打算半路打劫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.52,0:16:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼辦 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.10,0:16:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 幹掉他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.51,0:16:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.83,0:16:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這滑滑的是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.33,0:16:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛受傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.45,0:16:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散開
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.24,0:16:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包圍那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.69,0:16:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這查克拉的流動…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.72,0:16:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們的動作突然變得異常迅速
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.02,0:17:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結界術嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.59,0:17:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.28,0:17:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.19,0:17:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.16,0:17:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.09,0:17:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.52,0:17:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.73,0:17:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.88,0:17:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底打算跟我到哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.15,0:17:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到哪…不是你說走出這座森林嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.71,0:17:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話是這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.62,0:17:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 先前的要塞到村子之間
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.16,0:17:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真的就只有森林了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.89,0:17:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們都…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.79,0:17:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來我們的任務也快安全結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.75,0:18:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經抵達村子了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.13,0:18:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 人都去哪兒了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.85,0:18:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人嗎 有人在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.40,0:18:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐井
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.69,0:18:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.82,0:18:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螢回來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.19,0:18:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有人在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.14,0:18:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 稍等片刻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.98,0:18:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.66,0:19:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.25,0:19:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大事不好了 起火了 起火了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.65,0:19:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 果然還是有人在的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.51,0:19:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驚擾大家真是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.10,0:19:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰讓大家都不出來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.62,0:19:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得螢回來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.08,0:19:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一定會熱烈歡迎的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.00,0:19:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼了 大家都…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.29,0:19:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.18,0:19:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.84,0:19:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.51,0:19:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是這個村子的負責人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.06,0:19:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊急事態時的事也在役之行者那有所耳聞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.15,0:20:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後就交給我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.99,0:20:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我們就此告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.29,0:20:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等片刻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.72,0:20:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還未能表達敬意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.64,0:20:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.40,0:20:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的心意我們心領了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.10,0:20:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 還有夥伴留在了葛城山
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.05,0:20:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊…那就太可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.99,0:20:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我們快回去找小櫻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.70,0:20:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.97,0:20:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.42,0:20:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.05,0:20:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.45,0:20:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.44,0:20:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大和隊長 對不起 你們先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.10,0:20:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還要回趟那個村子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.94,0:21:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.17,0:21:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在是放心不下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.65,0:21:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些村民的眼神…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.93,0:21:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.36,0:21:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不能放任不管
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.47,0:22:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然說螢不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.47,0:22:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.29,0:22:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別太衝動了 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.07,0:22:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.37,0:22:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是同村的夥伴出了事 卻…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.60,0:22:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.48,0:22:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡發牢騷也不會有任何結果
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.57,0:23:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 現在當務之急是先找到她
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.55,0:23:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐井
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.36,0:23:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 這就展開搜索
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.41,0:23:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 火影忍者疾風傳
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.49,0:23:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼承者的意願
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.74,0:23:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著吧 我一定會把你找出來
